abstract: Jordan Spieth takes third round lead at Hyundai Tournament of Champions golf tournament in Kapalua, Hawaii; other golf news noted.
snippet: Jordan Spieth capped another strong performance with a 10-foot eagle for an eight-under-par 65, giving him a five-stroke lead over Brooks Koepka going into the final round of the Hyundai Tournament of Champions in Kapalua, Hawaii.
lead_paragraph: Jordan Spieth capped another strong performance with a 10-foot eagle for an eight-under-par 65, giving him a five-stroke lead over Brooks Koepka going into the final round of the Hyundai Tournament of Champions in Kapalua, Hawaii.
